1. enable xclip
1.1 install xclip from EPEL repo
1.2 enable ssh X11 forwarding
$ sudo yum install xorg-x11-xauth
1.3 install xclip
add to .bashrc:
    alias xclip="xclip -selection clipboard"
1.4 install vim-X11 to enable X11 clipboard in vim
$ sudo yum install vim-X11
add to .bashrc:
alias vim=vimx

2. install tmux 2.8 (default version is 1.8)
see 01-install-tmux-2.8
